# Coding Standards

## Naming
{% if 'Python' in languages -%}
- Variables/functions: snake_case, Classes: PascalCase, Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
{% elif 'TypeScript' in languages or 'Node.js' in languages -%}
- Variables/functions: camelCase, Classes/Components: PascalCase, Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
{% else -%}
- (define after choosing language)
{% endif %}

## Version Control
- Conventional Commits. One logical change per commit.

## Security
- Never hardcode secrets. Use .env files.
